((SELECT id FROM crops WHERE label = 'Turnip, Purple Top' and zone = 6),(SELECT id FROM data_keys WHERE label = 'cover_crop_description'),'Good forage, excellent for grazing. Potential for fast fall growth, high biomass, good N scavenging with adequate residual soil fertility. Cultivars can vary in bulb-vs.-leaf ratio, winter-hardiness, day-length response. Choose varieties that meet your needs. Big bulbs can be slow to break down, can interfere with subsequent operations like planting. Similar to radish/rapeseed, but much less taproot – instead makes bulb on surface. 
